Function Reference/in the loop « WordPress Codex
-----------

Whether the caller is in [The Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop") (i.e. whether
the loop is currently active).

Usage
-----

` <?php in_the_loop(); ?> `

Parameters
----------

none.

Return Value
------------

 `(boolean)` 
:   True if caller is within loop, false if loop hasn't started or has
    ended.

Changelog
---------

Since: 2.0.0

Source File
-----------

`comments_template()` is located in `wp-includes/query.php`.

